Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:03.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:11.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她知道知道我們淺賀商業街的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:12.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:16.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:18.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:20.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到處都是 煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 這回要讓你見識見識什麼叫天羅地網
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:24.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}目標在二丁目的十字路口向左跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:26.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我快受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很想用能力揍飛他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:31.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但要是讓雛知道的話就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:33.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:35.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,往這邊跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:37.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是追丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:39.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:41.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們還是應該找警察…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:42.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:45.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是非要找他們幫忙我還不如咬舌自盡算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:46.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,詩子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:00:59.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這兒
