Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:12.30,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:19.40,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:40.48,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在記憶之中 你微笑著的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:46.16,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡無奇的日常 是無可替的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:51.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}這份思念之情 現在終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.82,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你歡笑度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:56.63,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你爭論淚流的曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:00.99,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們攜手的每一天 令人無比憐愛的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:03.76,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:09.19,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:15.44,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回憶起你的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:20.25,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遙遙可見的那條街道的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:24.74,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露著笑容嗎
