Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:42.55,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(960,0)}第三話 流浪者生活之入門篇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:40.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是被黑社會給盯上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被盯上？ 應該沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:43.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:45.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還挺擔心的 這就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是個流浪漢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是你的前輩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:52.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你也被別人追著跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的做法不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,偷東西是犯法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:03.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像你這種行為是會被抓起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你有其他辦法生存嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請你告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看一下找零錢的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:21.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,10元啊 第一次撿就有運氣還真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這下邊也用棒子找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:32.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有的話 就再去撿罐子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行 裝滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:39.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這些罐子該怎麼處理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們去把這些換成錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還要走多長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們這些流浪者是要經常走路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,估計還要走兩小時吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼非要做這些事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:56.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟個傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你要過原來那種生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得能靠犯罪活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這些一共是690元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有這個 再去店裡就不會被追著跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:21.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這也能買3、4桶你剛才吃的泡麵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:26.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可我這一天走了這麼久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,賺錢可是很不容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在明白偷東西為什麼會被追了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天必須要給你辦個歡迎會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就用你今天賺的錢給大家買酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓他們接受你這個同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,流浪者就是要互相幫助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:58.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,除了今天我教你的 他們也會教你很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以把這些錢當作是學費
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了安叔 這孩子是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:08.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,重 她叫杏 今後就是我們中的一員了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什麼啊 這小鬼怎麼過得了這種生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先觀察她一段時間嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:20.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子用今天賺的錢 給大家買了酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你讓我喝那我就喝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:31.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,收這麼一個小孩子 安叔是怎麼想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:34.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是出了事 警察會盯上咱們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看 大家肯定都這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:40.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,重 還是先喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼 好像我就不能待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是我買的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:50.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣還不如我一個人待著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 好不容易開個酒會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唱首歌來聽聽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我要唱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:59.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 什麼都幹不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:02.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？ 連買酒的錢都是我出的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這些就估計要兩千塊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,估計是安叔把不夠的部分墊上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你有熟悉的歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 就會一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那能讓大叔們聽聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狼餓著肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:48.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到小鹿它就吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:52.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到小豬它就吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:57.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,它就吃吃吃 吃吃吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃到撐肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:05.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是我唱得太好聽把你們給感動了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:10.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 你唱得 真是難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:10.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起了我的孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個很愛唱歌的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什麼 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 抱歉 剛才對你的態度很差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喝點飲料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼你也哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是杏子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:51.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼沒回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:59.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還挺喜歡在這裡生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡這種生活？你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 就是打發打發時間而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這打發時間還挺高級的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能吃飽飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就帶了四萬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就先給你吧 記得好好吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:23.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,四 四 四萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:28.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別 別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會要你的施捨的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:36.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要自己賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵跟鋁的價格都跌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:46.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,錢越來越不好賺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去 不知道能不能挨過今年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:56.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她這麼精神 應該沒什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:00.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 好像有人在後面追我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:13.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:27.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然之間又想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我原本就打算給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道你想幹什麼 拿去花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那小鬼還在鞠著躬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有了這些錢 大家就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,終於抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在有錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我以後會付錢買東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:20.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的損失加起來一共是39340元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:22.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找你零錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我們就放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再做這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:33.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 你不用關心這些事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把錢全還上了 也挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:41.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說得對啊 不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:47.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我們這群人要是有了錢 就全都拿去買酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣你也沒了後顧之憂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就能開始全新的流浪漢生活了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:04.01,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs90\pos(1408,682)\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}超能力女兒
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.43,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(860,0)\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1396,502)}超能力女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:08.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早上好 我是三島瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,秋田縣部分地區在除夕舉行的民俗活動是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:13.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是生剝鬼節
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:14.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是生剝鬼節
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我這麼說有點自吹自擂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在學校裡的確是個認真的優等生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那只是我白天的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有個小秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:32.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一到晚上 我就會成為調酒師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要問這是為什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:39.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你穿這身衣服很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你什麼時候能來工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是我特地準備給你的嘛 來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我穿上看看我才穿上的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會付你時薪1500日元的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這對於普通的中學生來說可是很離譜的工資哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:01.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先對於普通的中學生而言打工就很離譜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:10.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把這張照片寄給你學校的話 會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:12.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什什什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:18.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想鬧出大問題的話就老實地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\bord0\c&H807E83&\frz2.013\pos(530,250)}錄音 新建錄音001
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是我特地準備給你的嘛 來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:24.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:27.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我有不祥的預感 就開了錄音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真有你的 小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近被捲進去的事有點多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:33.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經學乖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:34.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:37.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不互相留下把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要一起把數據都刪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不再威脅我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不會再威脅你了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我把衣服換回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:03.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,照片我早就傳到電腦去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您的代基里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:08.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,綜上所述 我開始了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:13.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:15.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經完全超越詩子小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您的讚美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:21.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是該笑的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,教導主任 我們也差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:28.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你再說什麼的 松谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚現在才開始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一個不錯的酒吧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:32.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再喝下去對身體不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想早點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,關於明年的年級主任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我跟校長強烈推薦你的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必讓我陪同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:52.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要死要死要死 怎麼辦怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎 小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,實 實際上是因為班主任來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:01.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,船到橋頭自然直啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那個 給我來杯馬提尼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:10.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:11.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:15.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.79,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80\3c&HB7B4BD&\shad5\bord4\b1\blur3\c&H342F30&\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\b0\4c&H848289&}為了不暴露自己 在努力地變臉中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:24.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太年輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:27.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 感覺超級眼熟的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:31.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三 三島？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:36.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請 請給我一杯百萬富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 冷靜下來 好險！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:40.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說都不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:41.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我難道醉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我教的學習認真的乖學生居然在做調酒師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太嚇人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:53.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷老師 超懷疑我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 松谷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個調酒師稍微 不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是相當像我教的一個學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你可糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:09.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真的 你年級主任的事就要吹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊是我認錯啦 還真有長得像的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:14.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:17.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼看都只是中學生而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥 你喝了就懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麼可是中學生調得出來的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小瞳可是超強的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:28.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三島她好像名字就是叫瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:31.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你個該死的蠢跟班仔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧既然都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:36.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我從學生時代開始就在各式各樣的酒吧工作過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我對味道可是很挑剔的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓他見識一下吧 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:45.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:08.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您的百萬富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,了 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是完美的搖酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒了解到她的攪拌技術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才稍微觀察了一下她的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她的手還沒有吧勺繭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說她雖然搖酒的技術還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但攪拌的火喉還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那您請下單
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:44.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 那就來一杯調酒師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您的調酒師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:06.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:10.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這等技術 在銀座一流的店裡也相當少見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且居然還沒有吧勺繭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就做得太多把繭弄沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這確實是中學生做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:27.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今後請務必繼續讓我品嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:33.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,變成了俘虜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,P.S. 瞞著父母開的賬戶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:51.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以驚人的氣勢進著錢 稍微讓我有點害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:00.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田你那邊的肉丸多了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:01.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,前陣子我遇到了杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:11.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要也學學杏子試試流浪生活？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 跟你比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和她一起住要好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:22.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還要再帶我來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 已經開始想下次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:29.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(276,800)\fs65\shad0\bord2\blur2\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&H342F30&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(738,630)}肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:31.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行行好吧 行行好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:30.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}吶 接下來想吃甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田你那邊的肉丸比較少哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還不是因為你昨天抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你可以拿走多出的那一個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:53.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天有會面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟過來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這是什麼情況！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:21.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 怎麼會 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:22.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我打掃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:26.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了新田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼不開心的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這蠢貨 眼淚這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:35.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,開心的時候也會流出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 買下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 要是再打碎的話我真的會幹死你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:15.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別打碎 絕對不能打碎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:24.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 這邊等下再打掃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:42.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8)\fn萝莉体 第二版\fs100\bord4\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H6E5C50&}獎勵雛時使用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:51.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,獎勵時用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:55.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也好好努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:56.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,準備作為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的晚飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得和以往的味道不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了新田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:12.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就是今天雛好像有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反常地把多出來的菜讓給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:17.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門的時候也特地到玄關來送我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就是說雛也有所成長了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天得獎她頓好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:28.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都有備好獎勵用的鮭魚子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她都沒做出值得表揚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都放壞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:50.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 肚子好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:55.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:02.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也要獎勵她一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:05.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
